<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[٩٨٦]</span> أَبُو بَرْزةَ الأَسْلَميُّ <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>اسْمُهُ نَضْلةُ بنُ عُبَيدٍ، لهُ صُحْبةٌ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[٩٨٧]</span> أَبُو مَعْبَدٍ، مَولَى ابنِ عَبّاسٍ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>سمِعَ ابنَ عَبّاسٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>رَوى عنهُ عَمرُو بنُ دِينارٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>اسمُهُ نَافِذٌ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[٩٨٨]</span> أَبُو ظِلالٍ القَسْمَليُّ الأَعْمَى <span class="c2">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>سَمِعَ أَنَسَ بنَ مَالِكٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>اسمُهُ هِلالٌ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[٩٨٩]</span> أَبُو بُرْدةَ بنُ نِيارٍ <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>اسمُهُ هَانئُ بنُ نِيارٍ، لهُ صُحْبةٌ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[٩٩٠]</span> أَبُو صَالحٍ <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>مَيسَرةُ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>عنْ عَلِيٍّ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>رَوى عنهُ عَطاءُ بنُ السَّائبِ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c4">[٩٩١]</span> أَبُو هاشِمٍ الرُّمَّانيُّ، وَاسِطيٌّ <span class="c2">(٦)</span>.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
